  names chipmunk libchipmunk
  hints
  env chipmunk_dir
  path_suffixes lib
  paths
  ~/library/frameworks
  /library/frameworks
  /usr/local
  /usr
  /sw
  /opt/local
  /opt/csw
  /opt
)
